    "name": "智械工厂 Desynced",
    "steam_appid": 1450900,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/638fff794abf9ac94e0c1ce2d9e19bc8.avif?t=1772164882\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《智械工厂》等待你来亲自启动！你需要不断推翻设计、修复漏洞、重构逻辑，直到整个系统真正稳定、高效、可持续运行。这不是简单的的建设任务，而是一场关于 智能、秩序与控制权 的长期实验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最终，你将不再是操作者——</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 你就是名副其实的智械主脑。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/98fecc67e5d6e95aaa2150c5ae758745.avif?t=1772164882\" width=780 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《智械工厂》中，传统的物流输送带与固定生产线不复存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取而代之的是一整套由 AI 智械驱动的自治工业网络。资源的采集、运输、分配与生产，全部交由智能机器人完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们不是被动执行命令的工具，而是根据环境与需求实时行动的智能体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的工厂不再是静态布局，而是一个持续运行、持续自我修正的动态系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/5c2cb8e8526e7b7d3c8be7b3f8ae3521.poster.avif?t=1772164882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/5c2cb8e8526e7b7d3c8be7b3f8ae3521.webm?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/5c2cb8e8526e7b7d3c8be7b3f8ae3521.mp4?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>当系统开始自行运转，工厂才真正诞生。</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/56914aed3cc0e90d4ac4d6e6e94a259e.avif?t=1772164882\" width=780 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将不再是简单的操作员，而是整个系统的<strong>架构师</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过可视化行为逻辑编译，为每一台机器人定义条件、优先级与执行规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需真正编程，却能够亲自定义机器人的逻辑判断、行为触发、系统协同、异常处理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/2df6ca6aaf6b6ab99cefb7c43822b7a1.poster.avif?t=1772164882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/2df6ca6aaf6b6ab99cefb7c43822b7a1.webm?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/2df6ca6aaf6b6ab99cefb7c43822b7a1.mp4?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>自然演化一直都能用一个词来描述——失败；这次，我们将亲自定义何为“成功”</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/29111d5bb64844a5f58ad7104bb1569e.avif?t=1772164882\" width=780 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里没有固定功能的建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一台机器、每一个设施，都是一个可被重新定义的平台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能源模块、采矿组件、扫描设备、生产单元…… 功能由你自由组合，结构由你自行决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一套系统，都是你为当前目标量身定制的解决方案</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/f6b7d25f280fe73f161882ae5e2fd40a.poster.avif?t=1772164882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/f6b7d25f280fe73f161882ae5e2fd40a.webm?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/f6b7d25f280fe73f161882ae5e2fd40a.mp4?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>最优解，从来不是前人制定好的模版，而是你亲自推演出来的设计。</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/4e870d3586e7524384bcee81bb3bee82.avif?t=1772164882\" width=780 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多变的地形、昼夜变化、环境威胁与未知区域，都会直接影响你的系统运作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，异星的有机体正在窥伺你的工厂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须为工业体系提供防护，清除异常生命体，确保系统持续运行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在扩张与探索中，逐步凑齐AI 觉醒的拼图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >铁人风暴即将席卷整颗星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/0f035594a3f565572b730e3201cce06d.poster.avif?t=1772164882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/0f035594a3f565572b730e3201cce06d.webm?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/0f035594a3f565572b730e3201cce06d.mp4?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>有机体！为时已晚 迎接肃清！</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/015a1df37cbc2578c616d41259d816d2.avif?t=1772164882\" width=780 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏支持本地与在线多人模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位玩家都可以负责不同的生产链、逻辑模块或扩张方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多名玩家共同维护、优化与重构的，不再是单一基地，而是一个<strong>巨型自治自动化网络</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协作、竞争、甚至彼此干扰，都会成为系统演化的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/dc81cbbbfc0363d0b81dade5394e0e30.poster.avif?t=1772164882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/dc81cbbbfc0363d0b81dade5394e0e30.webm?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450900/extras/dc81cbbbfc0363d0b81dade5394e0e30.mp4?t=1772164882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>当格式塔拥有多个主脑，系统将走向不可预测的未来。</u></i></p>",
